description: Redevelopment to create a ten storey (with basement) building providing flexible office floorspace (Class B1) at ground floor level and 110 private and affordable residential units across the upper floors (Class C3). Secure basement car and cycle parking and refuse storage provided at basement level accessed from a ramp on William Morris Way. Associated landscaping works to William Morris Way and Potters Road.
